{"timestamp": "2026-05-01T03:00:56.634022+00:00", "session_id": "71f1d2d8-1358-4b95-a8a7-f26fc0827908", "cwd": "/Users/toby/Documents/Projects/CodeIsland", "tool": "Edit", "input": {"file_path": "/Users/toby/.claude/projects/-Users-toby/memory/session-2026-05-01-mioserver-fix-codesisland-connect.md", "old_string": "### Socket.io path: `/v1/updates`\n- CodeIsland uses `connectParams` with token, Swift SocketIO library supports both auth object and query params\n- Server extracts: `socket.handshake.auth.token || socket.handshake.query.token`", "new_string": "### Socket.io path: `/v1/updates`\n- CodeIsland uses `connectParams` with token, Swift SocketIO library supports both auth object and query params\n- Server extracts: `socket.handshake.auth.token || socket.handshake.query.token`\n- CodeIsland \u4e3b\u52a8\u8fde Railway (WebSocket \u957f\u8fde\u63a5)\uff0c\u65e0\u9700\u7aef\u53e3\u6620\u5c04\n- \u670d\u52a1\u5668\u901a\u8fc7 eventRouter.push \u7ed9 Mac\uff0cMac \u4e5f\u901a\u8fc7\u540c\u4e00\u8fde\u63a5\u53d1\u6d88\u606f\n\n### Socket.io \u8fde\u63a5\u53c2\u6570 (ServerConnection.swift):\n```swift\nmanager = SocketManager(socketURL: url, config: [\n    .path(\"/v1/updates\"),\n    .connectParams([\"token\": token, \"clientType\": \"user-scoped\"]),\n    .reconnects(true),\n    .forceWebsockets(true),\n    .extraHeaders([\"Authorization\": \"Bearer \\(token)\"]),\n])\n```\n\u5b9e\u9645 URL: `wss://mio-server-production.up.railway.app/v1/updates/?token=xxx&clientType=user-scoped`\n\n### \u4e24\u5c42\u901a\u4fe1\u67b6\u6784:\n- **Mac \u2192 Server**: Socket.io \u957f\u8fde\u63a5 (\u4e3b\u52a8\u8fde Railway 443 \u7aef\u53e3)\n- **iPhone \u2192 Server**: HTTP \u8f6e\u8be2 GET /v1/sessions + Socket.io \u8fde\u63a5\n- **Server \u2192 Mac**: \u901a\u8fc7 eventRouter.push() \u63a8\u9001\u5230 Socket.io \u8fde\u63a5\n- **Server \u2192 iPhone**: HTTP \u54cd\u5e94 + Socket.io push", "replace_all": false}, "result": "PreToolUse"}
