{"timestamp": "2026-05-01T03:50:47.016035+00:00", "session_id": "71f1d2d8-1358-4b95-a8a7-f26fc0827908", "cwd": "/Users/toby/Documents/Projects/CodeIsland", "tool": "Bash", "input": {"command": "# Check if CodeIsland's JSONL watcher is getting any events from the hook\n# The hook log shows the session started: sid=89675e39\n# Let's see what sessions sync-daemon is actually syncing\n\ncd /Users/toby/Documents/Projects/CodeIsland/sync-daemon && cat state/offset_map.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); [print(k[:20],v) for k,v in d.items()]\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"no offset_map\"\n\n# Also check last few lines of daemon log\ncat /Users/toby/Documents/Projects/CodeIsland/sync-daemon/state/*.log 2>/dev/null | tail -20", "description": "Check sync-daemon state and recent activity"}, "result": "PreToolUse"}
